FBIS3-56333 "drsov010_a_94079" FBIS-SOV-94-010 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Jan 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Israeli Police Minister Meets With Yerin LD1301135594 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 0756 GMT 13 Jan 94 LD1301135594 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Moscow, 13 Jan (CRIME-PRESS) -- The Russian Internal Affairs Ministry's Public Relations Center reports that a meeting was held between Russia's Internal Affairs Minister Viktor Yerin and Moshe Shahal, Israel's minister of police and minister of energy and infrastructure, who is in Moscow on an official visit. During the conversation the problems of combating crime and the possibility of cooperation between the two countries in this sphere were touched upon. The signing of a protocol on the talks is scheduled for today.
